channel.title: Why Wont any of my Clients Download Cache?
channel.description: Ive downloaded many clients and they all fail on Cache and keeps saying error retrying in 5 seconds... why am i getting this so much and nothing works?

item.title: Why Wont any of my Clients Download Cache?
item.dc:creator: @Korres Korres
item.description:
@Korres wrote:

Try downloading a client from the server status page to someone else’s server and see if it downloads the cache. If it downloads fine, then the client’s you are downloading may have something wrong with the link, or the link might be down to the cache. Try to download clients that include the cache.
